'''彼得·道格拉斯·沃德'''（{{lang-en|Peter Douglas Ward}}，{{bd|1949年|}}）是一位美国[[古生物学|古生物学]]家和科普作家，现为[[澳大利亚|澳大利亚]][[阿德莱德大学|阿德莱德大学]]教授，主要贡献有提出了[[美狄亚假说|美狄亚假说]]（Medea hypothesis）、[[地球殊異假說|地球殊異假說]]（Rare Earth hypothesis，与[[唐纳德·E·布朗利|唐纳德·E·布朗利]]共同提出<ref name=Williams2020-07-29-01a>{{cite web|url=https://www.gazzetta.it/Giroditalia/2014/download/Regolamento_Ing.pdf/|author=Matt Williams|publisher=[[Universe_Today|Universe Today]]|title=Beyond "Fermi's Paradox" IV: What is the Rare Earth Hypothesis?|date=29 July 2020|accessdate=6 June 2021|quote=Origins: The term “Rare Earth” takes its name from the book Rare Earth: Why Complex Life Is Uncommon in the Universe (2000), by Peter Ward and Donald E. Brownlee ... As the authors describe it, the Rare Earth argument comes down to two central hypotheses ... making Earth a very special place|archive-date=2020-11-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201128051948/https://www.gazzetta.it/Giroditalia/2014/download/Regolamento_Ing.pdf}}</ref> ）等，另外也出版了多部科普著作<ref>{{cite web|url=http://microbes-mind.net/advisers.html|title=Advisers, Microbe Mind Forum|url-status=dead|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140228170953/http://microbes-mind.net/advisers.html|archivedate=2014-02-28}}</ref>。

